Bumps <https://github.com/rubocop/rubocop|rubocop> from 1.57.1 to 1.57.2.

Release notes

_Sourced from <https://github.com/rubocop/rubocop/releases|rubocop's releases>._

> *RuboCop 1.57.2*
> *Bug fixes*
> 
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12274|#12274>: Fix a false positive for `Lint/Void` when `each`'s receiver is an object of `Enumerator` to which `filter` has been applied. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12291|#12291>: Fix a false positive for `Metrics/ClassLength` when a class with a singleton class definition. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12293|#12293>: Fix a false positive for `Style/RedundantDoubleSplatHashBraces` when using double splat hash braces with `merge` and method chain. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12298|#12298>: Fix a false positive for `Style/RedundantParentheses` when using a parenthesized hash literal as the first argument in a method call without parentheses. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/pull/12283|#12283>: Fix an error for `Style/SingleLineDoEndBlock` when using single line `do`...`end` with no body. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12312|#12312>: Fix an incorrect autocorrect for `Style/HashSyntax` when braced hash key and value are the same and it is used in `if`...`else`. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12307|#12307>: Fix an infinite loop error for `Layout/EndAlignment` when `EnforcedStyleAlignWith: variable` and using a conditional statement in a method argument on the same line and `end` with method call is not aligned. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/11652|#11652>: Make `--auto-gen-config` generate `inherit_from` correctly inside ERB `if`. (<https://github.com/jonas054|`@​jonas054`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12310|#12310>: Drop `base64` gem from runtime dependency. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12300|#12300>: Fix an error for `Style/IdenticalConditionalBranches` when `if`...`else` with identical leading lines and using index assign. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12286|#12286>: Fix false positives for `Style/RedundantDoubleSplatHashBraces` when using double splat with a hash literal enclosed in parenthesized ternary operator. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12279|#12279>: Fix false positives for `Lint/EmptyConditionalBody` when missing 2nd `if` body with a comment. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12275|#12275>: Fix a false positive for `Style/RedundantDoubleSplatHashBraces` when using double splat within block argument containing a hash literal in an array literal. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12284|#12284>: Fix false positives for `Style/SingleArgumentDig` when using some anonymous argument syntax. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
> • <https://redirect.github.com/rubocop/rubocop/issues/12301|#12301>: Make `Style/RedundantFilterChain` aware of safe navigation operator. (<https://github.com/koic|`@​koic`>)
